                    <p style="color: #555; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.1rem;">An optimization of legume-based protein metrics. By processing canned or soaked chickpeas into a deep caramel onion-and-tomato reduction, we unlock highly dense, fiber-rich nutritional value while eliminating expensive secondary protein parameters.</p>

